<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>写作助手 with AI · 下载</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico">
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: -apple-system, "PingFang SC", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
      background: #fafafa;
      color: #222;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    main {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 32px 20px;
    }
    header h1 { margin: 0 0 4px; font-size: 28px; }
    header p.lede { color: #555; margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 14px; }

    .card {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 20px 22px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .card.badge-release { border-left: 4px solid #2e7d32; }
    .card.badge-debug   { border-left: 4px solid #f57c00; }

    .card-head {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .card-head h2 { margin: 0; font-size: 20px; }
    .muted { color: #888; font-weight: normal; font-size: 14px; }

    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 2px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .badge.badge-release { background: #2e7d32; }
    .badge.badge-debug   { background: #f57c00; }

    .tagline { color: #666; font-size: 13px; margin: 4px 0 14px; }

    .btn-download {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #3370ff;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 12px 28px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .btn-download:hover { background: #245bdb; }

    .meta {
      margin-top: 12px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #555;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
    .meta code {
      background: #f0f0f0;
      padding: 1px 6px;
      border-radius: 3px;
      font-size: 12px;
      word-break: break-all;
    }

    details {
      margin-top: 12px;
      border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
      padding-top: 8px;
    }
    details summary {
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: 500;
      outline: none;
      color: #444;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    details pre, details p {
      margin: 8px 0;
      white-space: pre-wrap;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    details ul { padding-left: 20px; margin: 8px 0; }
    details li { margin: 4px 0; font-size: 13px; }

    .qr {
      margin-top: 24px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #666;
    }
    .qr img {
      width: 160px;
      height: 160px;
      display: block;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }
    footer {
      margin-top: 48px;
      padding-top: 16px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #999;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main>
    <header>
      <h1>写作助手 with AI</h1>
      <p class="lede">原生 Android 笔记 + AI 助手,自托管 APK 分发。</p>
    </header>

    {{CHANNEL_CARDS}}

    <p class="qr">
      扫码下载 ↓(扫描当前页 URL)
      <br>
      <img src="/app/release/qr.png" alt="下载二维码">
    </p>

    <footer>
      <p>本应用走自托管 APK 分发,仅供内测使用。详见
      <a href="https://github.com/shaoyahu/writing-with-ai">项目主页</a>。</p>
    </footer>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
